** ht1621_lcd_type: supported types:
 none              : -
 denver_tr36       : LCD from radio 'Denver TR36'
 grundig_boy       : LCD from radio 'Grundig Prima Boy 100'
 check             : all segments on (debug / investigation)

** grundig_boy100
 Especially for an extra designed pcb using in an grundig prima boy 100
 radio. This option will set automated these options:
  ht1621_lcd_type = grundig_boy
  grundig_matrix_button = true
  pin_ht1621_data = 13
  pin_ht1621_cs = 14
  pin_ht1621_wr = 16
